title: Jordan river so chilly and cold,
lyrics: Jordan river so chilly and cold, It chills my body but not my soul, Jordan river so chilly and cold, It chills my body but not my soul And every time I feel the Spirit Moving in me l want to pray, And every time l feel the Spirit Moving in me l want to pray.
